  {
    "id": "1e84f82a-5353-8086-8c4a-dd0893205489",
    "title": "Delete Button Case Study",
    "slug": "delete-button-case-study",
    "date": "March 24, 2026",
    "category": "General",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "The Challenge"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Destructive actions (e.g., deleting accounts or data) are irreversible, yet many interfaces design them poorly—leading to accidental data loss, frustrated users, and eroded trust."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "img",
        "url": "https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/052b5715-3363-4fe6-980e-3f0dd8222353/45de24ac-e02e-4208-97a1-a35f24d0fce6/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466W6VZZRKN%2F20260329%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20260329T185252Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEEsaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIAiyLi8DW88MBdvcBUcgGYe%2BWotn3J5pBXHPA%2B4AByP2AiEA7zJDGq6GgjdavjM4fh99ALMQikBcHD0Fgm%2FOzcuss9Uq%2FwMIFBAAGgw2Mzc0MjMxODM4MDUiDMLAlCXYJq5BREUnsircA%2FUciuHnBtBP0uTqseWBt4Q%2BwQaKXLILf0RwtYQATs8Fkg43DrNlwuezYHLnWjZz48XZcbZ%2FDmT5nWU8rktZIe88GMmeCn9RTUAU%2B1xTJlIJGaQxy01k9rMqtfi01WbQkWJwfAmV6idXGnpDlI1732qYZAWciAsoum86dUB%2FYw4IXlG04csEMPuCuTrqCODsPb1sML9C3m7vBgy3lc2NQESV03zHwsoW2EuLTYAqi2YHIgyQqUHZ1oeT8GcVP2XcGT%2BKKwSSq%2FHPYXi0W%2B%2B9IanQJJzIkXduzFb9sR7cBtSE9Ww%2Fiv0dshHFpGzP%2F0V5z7uErJcLNTlx42zRXhxoXk1M2hmTYYuipzAotnT51QXlztv1HJz%2BtAy27Hpqr3lTuWsvR%2FwCm7KyYdTToKijVjf3mKK7X3CemUZ8RdnADlSmdnEOI1nKwow7UFNDGwXcQUZvsHaI2oESrJtHyY9XObntVvekQ7i5JZ58eslpz3gJwEoOnB0RDYkBUcrzWV2JzReavJNZvvUA9F%2BlZ0jQUQaZF9TWS%2F6qDa%2F8y41UXiJnE9yBj7G5PJhiSPZ%2Br1aZtixrvmW02w3oqLBs95O2DtmjhPa0dfl7B1%2B5e9fXDGOkQtJ6pZgZ0UypP%2FkVMKXlpc4GOqUBpH6hfOYSiWtQYqcnyUhnfa5W%2FF8eUEb5ykLQeMVGo0VcNd4%2FJqJiGSI3Joq%2F3vS7bDKOvR9dbY50Uks%2FjWwpEWMdFalTlNmBsq1EgF2EjPjimNJD36HMQDi1BUphRXHu5Zug3DoWF2inybZgNKTK%2B4ikK8kHF%2Fgt7lmDfOZa77HwzEKFn90DMg3cTCpn58LuCCYYaZAizOnXTafXUg67ey3b2qFB&X-Amz-Signature=a7da0e874d87a2500ce1f072a504adcc93ed8e10bbe25ef7cdbf80cbbdf14d5a&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&x-id=GetObject",
        "caption": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "Key Problems Identified"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Poorly designed dialog: Unclear \"Proceed\" button, no visible cancel option"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Example of problematic design: Ambiguous labels, low contrast, and missing safeguards."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Ambiguous labels (\"Proceed\" instead of \"Delete Account\").",
        "listType": "number"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "No confirmation dialogs, allowing irreversible actions to trigger instantly.",
        "listType": "number"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Accessibility failures: Low contrast, small click targets, missing focus states.",
        "listType": "number"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Inconsistent patterns across platforms (desktop vs. mobile).",
        "listType": "number"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "img",
        "url": "https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/052b5715-3363-4fe6-980e-3f0dd8222353/fa5eebab-431e-4d43-95cb-1796b8e0dedd/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466W6VZZRKN%2F20260329%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20260329T185252Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEEsaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIAiyLi8DW88MBdvcBUcgGYe%2BWotn3J5pBXHPA%2B4AByP2AiEA7zJDGq6GgjdavjM4fh99ALMQikBcHD0Fgm%2FOzcuss9Uq%2FwMIFBAAGgw2Mzc0MjMxODM4MDUiDMLAlCXYJq5BREUnsircA%2FUciuHnBtBP0uTqseWBt4Q%2BwQaKXLILf0RwtYQATs8Fkg43DrNlwuezYHLnWjZz48XZcbZ%2FDmT5nWU8rktZIe88GMmeCn9RTUAU%2B1xTJlIJGaQxy01k9rMqtfi01WbQkWJwfAmV6idXGnpDlI1732qYZAWciAsoum86dUB%2FYw4IXlG04csEMPuCuTrqCODsPb1sML9C3m7vBgy3lc2NQESV03zHwsoW2EuLTYAqi2YHIgyQqUHZ1oeT8GcVP2XcGT%2BKKwSSq%2FHPYXi0W%2B%2B9IanQJJzIkXduzFb9sR7cBtSE9Ww%2Fiv0dshHFpGzP%2F0V5z7uErJcLNTlx42zRXhxoXk1M2hmTYYuipzAotnT51QXlztv1HJz%2BtAy27Hpqr3lTuWsvR%2FwCm7KyYdTToKijVjf3mKK7X3CemUZ8RdnADlSmdnEOI1nKwow7UFNDGwXcQUZvsHaI2oESrJtHyY9XObntVvekQ7i5JZ58eslpz3gJwEoOnB0RDYkBUcrzWV2JzReavJNZvvUA9F%2BlZ0jQUQaZF9TWS%2F6qDa%2F8y41UXiJnE9yBj7G5PJhiSPZ%2Br1aZtixrvmW02w3oqLBs95O2DtmjhPa0dfl7B1%2B5e9fXDGOkQtJ6pZgZ0UypP%2FkVMKXlpc4GOqUBpH6hfOYSiWtQYqcnyUhnfa5W%2FF8eUEb5ykLQeMVGo0VcNd4%2FJqJiGSI3Joq%2F3vS7bDKOvR9dbY50Uks%2FjWwpEWMdFalTlNmBsq1EgF2EjPjimNJD36HMQDi1BUphRXHu5Zug3DoWF2inybZgNKTK%2B4ikK8kHF%2Fgt7lmDfOZa77HwzEKFn90DMg3cTCpn58LuCCYYaZAizOnXTafXUg67ey3b2qFB&X-Amz-Signature=5209e419e4720eebf1f84212eec5eb6896d9afb730341292e4c7424d93fd6eeb&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&x-id=GetObject",
        "caption": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "Goals"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Prevent accidental destructive actions.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Ensure destructive buttons are fully accessible (WCAG 2.1 Level AA compliant).",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Create a consistent, predictable pattern across all products.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Educate internal teams on the importance of accessible destructive design.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "Approach"
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "🔍 User Testing & Heuristic Analysis"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "We conducted usability testing and heuristic evaluations on key interfaces (e.g., account settings, file managers). Key findings included:"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Users skipped warning text due to poor contrast or vague language.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Keyboard users struggled to locate the active button due to missing focus indicators.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "On mobile, destructive buttons were too close to primary actions like “Save.”",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "img",
