      {
        "type": "h2",
        "text": "Solutions & Design Decisions"
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "Clear, Action-Oriented Labels"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Problem: Vague labels like “Proceed” confused users."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Solution:"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "We replaced ambiguous labels with explicit action verbs, such as:"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "“Delete My Account”",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "“Remove User”",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "“Cancel Subscription”",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "This increased user understanding and reduced hesitation during task completion."
      },
      {
        "type": "img",
        "url": "https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/052b5715-3363-4fe6-980e-3f0dd8222353/30e0ed24-8739-4698-b69a-77c2fde27af7/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466W6VZZRKN%2F20260329%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20260329T185253Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEEsaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIAiyLi8DW88MBdvcBUcgGYe%2BWotn3J5pBXHPA%2B4AByP2AiEA7zJDGq6GgjdavjM4fh99ALMQikBcHD0Fgm%2FOzcuss9Uq%2FwMIFBAAGgw2Mzc0MjMxODM4MDUiDMLAlCXYJq5BREUnsircA%2FUciuHnBtBP0uTqseWBt4Q%2BwQaKXLILf0RwtYQATs8Fkg43DrNlwuezYHLnWjZz48XZcbZ%2FDmT5nWU8rktZIe88GMmeCn9RTUAU%2B1xTJlIJGaQxy01k9rMqtfi01WbQkWJwfAmV6idXGnpDlI1732qYZAWciAsoum86dUB%2FYw4IXlG04csEMPuCuTrqCODsPb1sML9C3m7vBgy3lc2NQESV03zHwsoW2EuLTYAqi2YHIgyQqUHZ1oeT8GcVP2XcGT%2BKKwSSq%2FHPYXi0W%2B%2B9IanQJJzIkXduzFb9sR7cBtSE9Ww%2Fiv0dshHFpGzP%2F0V5z7uErJcLNTlx42zRXhxoXk1M2hmTYYuipzAotnT51QXlztv1HJz%2BtAy27Hpqr3lTuWsvR%2FwCm7KyYdTToKijVjf3mKK7X3CemUZ8RdnADlSmdnEOI1nKwow7UFNDGwXcQUZvsHaI2oESrJtHyY9XObntVvekQ7i5JZ58eslpz3gJwEoOnB0RDYkBUcrzWV2JzReavJNZvvUA9F%2BlZ0jQUQaZF9TWS%2F6qDa%2F8y41UXiJnE9yBj7G5PJhiSPZ%2Br1aZtixrvmW02w3oqLBs95O2DtmjhPa0dfl7B1%2B5e9fXDGOkQtJ6pZgZ0UypP%2FkVMKXlpc4GOqUBpH6hfOYSiWtQYqcnyUhnfa5W%2FF8eUEb5ykLQeMVGo0VcNd4%2FJqJiGSI3Joq%2F3vS7bDKOvR9dbY50Uks%2FjWwpEWMdFalTlNmBsq1EgF2EjPjimNJD36HMQDi1BUphRXHu5Zug3DoWF2inybZgNKTK%2B4ikK8kHF%2Fgt7lmDfOZa77HwzEKFn90DMg3cTCpn58LuCCYYaZAizOnXTafXUg67ey3b2qFB&X-Amz-Signature=b8a6cfec8f20f1f882313ec356e42495f760a5ade77aebf1d880440614de5930&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&x-id=GetObject",
        "caption": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "✅ 2. Confirmation Dialogs"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Problem: Actions occurred immediately without warnings."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Solution:"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "We introduced confirmation modals that included:"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Clear warning messages about consequences",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Optional checkboxes for sensitive deletions",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Clear button options: “Cancel” (non-destructive), “Confirm Delete” (destructive)",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "✅ 3. Visual Differentiation"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Problem: Destructive buttons visually blended with other controls."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Solution:"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Used high-contrast red color with text + icon (e.g., 🗑️ DELETE)",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Avoided placing destructive actions next to primary buttons",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Styled destructive actions as secondary, except within confirmation dialogs",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "✅ 4. Accessibility Compliance"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Problem: Buttons failed to meet basic WCAG standards."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Solution:"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "We updated destructive buttons to meet:"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Target size of at least 24×24px (WCAG 2.5.8)",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Contrast ratio ≥ 4.5:1 between text and background (WCAG 1.4.3)",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Focus visibility (WCAG 2.4.7) with clear outlines and spacing",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "We also tested with assistive technologies to ensure compatibility."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "Results"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "92% reduction in support tickets related to accidental deletion.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Improved task completion rates in usability tests.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Positive qualitative feedback from users: “I feel much safer using this now.”",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Design system updated with clear patterns for destructive actions, adopted across multiple teams.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "Key Takeaways"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Destructive buttons must be designed with caution: clear labels, confirmation dialogs, and accessible styles are non-negotiable.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Accessibility is not a layer on top—it’s part of the design from the beginning.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Small improvements (like button spacing and contrast) significantly impact user trust and safety.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      }
    ],
